00:02:52.874 --> 00:02:54.441 position:33% line:83% align:start
We were both
just a little awkward

00:02:54.575 --> 00:02:55.843 position:24% line:89% align:start
around each other.

00:02:56.276 --> 00:02:58.546 position:27% line:83% align:start
We thought hiding
our emotions was healthy.

00:02:58.980 --> 00:03:01.716 position:10% line:83% align:start
Like we could keep each other
safe from our pain.

00:03:03.084 --> 00:03:05.687 position:10% line:89% align:start
So, tell me, Mama. Be honest.

00:03:06.386 --> 00:03:08.255 position:33% line:83% align:start
I wanna know
how you really feel.

00:03:08.690 --> 00:03:10.758 position:35% line:83% align:start
And please,
don't hold anything back.

00:03:11.258 --> 00:03:14.762 position:27% line:83% align:start
When I was young,
was I a good kid?

00:03:15.797 --> 00:03:18.132 position:35% line:83% align:start
Were you...
What do you mean?

00:03:18.766 --> 00:03:22.335 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're perfect.
It was me who...

00:03:23.504 --> 00:03:26.040 position:38% line:83% align:start
