to help with that!

00:03:28.643 --> 00:03:31.713 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
I remember that day

00:03:32.180 --> 00:03:33.915 position:30% line:89% align:start
when we were...

00:03:35.382 --> 00:03:36.751 position:38% line:83% align:start
