00:03:45.827 --> 00:03:47.427 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's not okay!

00:03:48.029 --> 00:03:49.530 position:16% line:89% align:start
Quit trying to take her.

00:03:49.697 --> 00:03:51.833 position:7% line:89% align:start
'Cause she has me by her side!

00:03:52.432 --> 00:03:55.268 position:38% line:83% align:start
