00:03:59.607 --> 00:04:00.942 position:16% line:89% align:start
But pretend it's nothing!

00:04:01.142 --> 00:04:04.011 position:19% line:83% align:start
Don't forget, no matter
what else happens,

00:04:04.145 --> 00:04:07.215 position:13% line:83% align:start
what kind of world did you
dream of making, again?

00:04:07.347 --> 00:04:09.282 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:04:10.752 --> 00:04:12.419 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
Yes, right.

00:04:13.788 --> 00:04:15.489 position:27% line:89% align:start
The dream I had.

00:04:16.389 --> 00:04:17.290 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

