00:04:31.304 --> 00:04:32.607 position:35% line:89% align:start
[rumbling]

00:04:32.740 --> 00:04:35.610 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:04:37.712 --> 00:04:40.148 position:24% line:83% align:start
