00:04:43.818 --> 00:04:46.419 position:33% line:83% align:start
So much power
coming from her pain.

00:04:47.088 --> 00:04:48.321 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mama.

00:04:49.389 --> 00:04:51.324 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh.
-[SHY] Pepesha,

00:04:51.626 --> 00:04:54.061 position:13% line:89% align:start
