she's buried in her misery.

00:05:08.242 --> 00:05:10.511 position:30% line:89% align:start
[fire roaring]

00:05:10.678 --> 00:05:12.479 position:21% line:89% align:start
Or how bad it seems.

00:05:13.848 --> 00:05:15.616 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[SHY] We'll rescue her!
-[SPIRIT] We'll rescue her!

00:05:17.552 --> 00:05:18.553 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KUFUFU]
Watch out!

00:05:18.953 --> 00:05:21.088 position:30% line:83% align:start
-I'm freezing.
-[crackling]

00:05:23.423 --> 00:05:25.526 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:05:25.760 --> 00:05:27.161 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
