the strength left to shiver.

00:05:30.965 --> 00:05:33.366 position:33% line:89% align:start
[shattering]

00:05:33.501 --> 00:05:36.070 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA] It doesn't matter!
Nothing does!

00:05:36.204 --> 00:05:37.238 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:05:37.738 --> 00:05:40.208 position:38% line:83% align:start
[groans]
Don't get any closer!

00:05:40.608 --> 00:05:42.143 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
I have one wish.

00:05:42.310 --> 00:05:43.945 position:16% line:89% align:start
Is that too much to ask?

00:05:44.078 --> 00:05:45.112 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:05:46.047 --> 00:05:48.516 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

00:05:49.050 --> 00:05:52.286 position:16% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA] I just want this
frozen world to leave me alone.

00:05:52.485 --> 00:05:53.855 position:33% line:89% align:start
To disappear.

00:05:53.988 --> 00:05:55.022 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mama!

00:05:56.991 --> 00:05:58.926 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Who am I fighting for?

00:06:00.194 --> 00:06:01.729 position:16% line:89% align:start
