00:06:25.385 --> 00:06:26.787 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Welcome to life.

00:06:27.221 --> 00:06:28.823 position:21% line:89% align:start
My precious daughter.

00:06:29.090 --> 00:06:31.025 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:06:31.158 --> 00:06:32.126 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Pesha.

00:06:32.260 --> 00:06:39.499 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:06:45.973 --> 00:06:47.675 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
I'm still with you.

00:06:49.442 --> 00:06:50.945 position:27% line:89% align:start
You aren't alone.

00:06:51.345 --> 00:06:55.082 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:06:55.216 --> 00:06:56.384 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
See?

