00:07:02.957 --> 00:07:05.026 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:07:07.427 --> 00:07:10.331 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:07:10.463 --> 00:07:11.866 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
My mama was a type.

00:07:12.432 --> 00:07:14.502 position:7% line:89% align:start
She was always stoic and cool.

00:07:15.536 --> 00:07:16.704 position:30% line:83% align:start
But there were
some nights she'd laugh

00:07:16.837 --> 00:07:18.272 position:19% line:89% align:start
like a cute little kid,

00:07:18.940 --> 00:07:21.208 position:19% line:83% align:start
and we'd keep chatting
until we fell asleep.

00:07:22.510 --> 00:07:23.744 position:33% line:89% align:start
Those nights.

00:07:25.746 --> 00:07:27.447 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wind whooshing]

00:07:27.748 --> 00:07:29.517 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:07:34.655 --> 00:07:36.456 position:21% line:83% align:start
