your attention, Pepesha?

00:07:36.624 --> 00:07:37.858 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:07:38.592 --> 00:07:41.162 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hm. That's a photo
of Lenya, huh?

00:07:42.462 --> 00:07:45.066 position:27% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT] [crying]
Did mama...

00:07:45.866 --> 00:07:47.935 position:10% line:89% align:start
Did she not want me anymore?

00:07:48.736 --> 00:07:50.104 position:30% line:89% align:start
