was an accident.

00:07:57.477 --> 00:08:00.915 position:13% line:83% align:start
Make no mistake, she loved
you more than words can say.

00:08:01.415 --> 00:08:02.550 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're wrong.

00:08:03.017 --> 00:08:05.920 position:21% line:83% align:start
