and that's why she's gone now.

00:08:06.320 --> 00:08:07.555 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:08:09.390 --> 00:08:10.624 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here.

00:08:13.794 --> 00:08:15.495 position:7% line:89% align:start
