00:08:33.214 --> 00:08:35.516 position:27% line:83% align:start
Lenya was no good
at holding her liquor.

00:08:36.017 --> 00:08:39.286 position:10% line:83% align:start
So, I have my doubts that she
could remember writing to us.

00:08:39.754 --> 00:08:42.156 position:33% line:83% align:start
That lady was
positively hopeless.

