00:09:06.647 --> 00:09:08.282 position:27% line:89% align:start
Of course, I can!

00:09:09.650 --> 00:09:12.653 position:24% line:83% align:start
[laughs] Then maybe
I've had too much.

00:09:13.821 --> 00:09:15.423 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Yeah, that's right.

00:09:15.956 --> 00:09:18.692 position:30% line:83% align:start
When she drank,
she'd laugh like a kid,

00:09:19.060 --> 00:09:20.828 position:27% line:83% align:start
