to each other.

00:09:21.829 --> 00:09:24.165 position:16% line:83% align:start
She'd play around with me
like we were friends,

00:09:24.799 --> 00:09:26.600 position:7% line:89% align:start
and we let ourselves act silly.

00:09:27.668 --> 00:09:29.270 position:16% line:89% align:start
So, I remember thinking,

00:09:30.371 --> 00:09:32.006 position:21% line:89% align:start
"Alcohol is magical."

00:09:32.406 --> 00:09:33.974 position:16% line:89% align:start
It has mystic properties

00:09:34.275 --> 00:09:36.610 position:27% line:83% align:start
that turn adults
back into kids.

00:09:37.745 --> 00:09:39.046 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Say, Pesha.

00:09:39.548 --> 00:09:41.148 position:16% line:89% align:start
I know a wonderful place.

00:09:41.516 --> 00:09:44.185 position:19% line:83% align:start
The kind of place where
you'll never go hungry,

00:09:44.485 --> 00:09:47.321 position:21% line:83% align:start
and every day is full
of happiness and warmth.

00:09:48.089 --> 00:09:50.157 position:24% line:83% align:start
Would you wanna go
to a place like that?

00:09:51.492 --> 00:09:53.427 position:10% line:89% align:start
Would you be there too, Mama?

00:09:53.828 --> 00:09:56.230 position:35% line:83% align:start
No, adults
aren't allowed there.

00:09:57.465 --> 00:09:58.699 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:09:59.433 --> 00:10:01.735 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[LETANA] Well?
-Unh-uh.

00:10:02.571 --> 00:10:03.671 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Why not?

00:10:04.405 --> 00:10:06.974 position:24% line:83% align:start
I wouldn't be happy
anywhere without you.

00:10:07.108 --> 00:10:08.142 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:10:09.443 --> 00:10:10.811 position:35% line:89% align:start
Is that so?

00:10:11.580 --> 00:10:13.380 position:10% line:89% align:start
Your mama feels the same way.

00:10:14.415 --> 00:10:17.586 position:16% line:83% align:start
[LETANA] Pesha, after you
become an adult,

00:10:18.319 --> 00:10:20.621 position:24% line:83% align:start
let's have a drink
as mother and daughter.

00:10:21.722 --> 00:10:24.391 position:21% line:83% align:start
And then we can laugh
the night away,

00:10:24.758 --> 00:10:27.194 position:21% line:83% align:start
and have as much fun
as we did today.

00:10:27.962 --> 00:10:30.631 position:27% line:83% align:start
That's a promise
from me to you.

00:10:31.398 --> 00:10:33.968 position:30% line:83% align:start
I hope you love
your life as an adult,

00:10:34.935 --> 00:10:37.705 position:30% line:83% align:start
but until then,
stay a kid for me.

00:10:41.576 --> 00:10:42.810 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Mama.

00:10:44.912 --> 00:10:46.847 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh.
-Oh, of course.

00:10:47.414 --> 00:10:49.383 position:24% line:83% align:start
[NATALIA] She sent
this with the caption,

00:10:49.518 --> 00:10:50.751 position:24% line:89% align:start
"This is my dream."

00:10:51.152 --> 00:10:52.786 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's the future she wanted,

00:10:53.087 --> 00:10:55.055 position:21% line:83% align:start
where the two of you
are full of happiness,

00:10:55.222 --> 00:10:58.659 position:24% line:83% align:start
and even more full
of delicious food and love.

00:11:01.395 --> 00:11:02.564 position:27% line:89% align:start
See what I mean?

00:11:02.763 --> 00:11:04.765 position:19% line:89% align:start
She wants you to smile.

00:11:05.966 --> 00:11:07.835 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Uh-uh look.

00:11:08.335 --> 00:11:09.270 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:09.403 --> 00:11:10.971 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's not because I'm full.
[sobbing]

00:11:11.506 --> 00:11:12.773 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm not smiling

00:11:13.307 --> 00:11:15.743 position:21% line:83% align:start
because I don't feel
hungry anymore.

00:11:15.910 --> 00:11:18.112 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm smiling
because mama's there.

00:11:18.245 --> 00:11:19.914 position:38% line:83% align:start
[crying]
I should've said...

00:11:20.247 --> 00:11:22.149 position:10% line:89% align:start
I didn't care if we had food.

00:11:22.716 --> 00:11:24.619 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll never be able
to let her know.

00:11:24.752 --> 00:11:27.589 position:27% line:83% align:start
I still loved her
no matter what we had.

00:11:27.788 --> 00:11:31.025 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

00:11:36.363 --> 00:11:38.265 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
My life changed after that day.

00:11:39.166 --> 00:11:41.769 position:16% line:83% align:start
But some things inside me
will never change.

00:11:42.604 --> 00:11:43.704 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're still there,

00:11:44.305 --> 00:11:46.240 position:33% line:83% align:start
and the love
you gave me is too.

00:11:47.609 --> 00:11:50.311 position:19% line:83% align:start
But your love was more
than I could keep to myself.

00:11:51.245 --> 00:11:53.447 position:16% line:83% align:start
So, I wanted to spread it
around the world.

00:11:55.182 --> 00:11:57.818 position:33% line:83% align:start
Before long,
people called me a Hero.

00:11:59.086 --> 00:12:01.322 position:30% line:83% align:start
But the source
of my love hasn't changed.

00:12:01.889 --> 00:12:03.724 position:24% line:83% align:start
Regardless of what
life throws at me,

00:12:03.991 --> 00:12:07.328 position:21% line:83% align:start
it's always been you.
It always will be.

00:12:11.031 --> 00:12:12.399 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Do you understand?

00:12:13.167 --> 00:12:14.835 position:24% line:89% align:start
I hope I was clear.

00:12:15.970 --> 00:12:17.706 position:19% line:83% align:start
These are the feelings
I've always wanted

00:12:17.838 --> 00:12:19.206 position:24% line:89% align:start
to share with you.

00:12:20.407 --> 00:12:23.010 position:30% line:83% align:start
I guess there's
one more thing to say.

00:12:23.578 --> 00:12:25.647 position:19% line:83% align:start
Though I've never been
good at this part.

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:29.116 position:10% line:83% align:start
But please, give me a chance
to say it anyway.

00:12:31.285 --> 00:12:32.319 position:35% line:89% align:start
I love you.

00:12:32.820 --> 00:12:33.754 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mama.

00:12:33.887 --> 00:12:36.490 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:12:41.495 --> 00:12:42.796 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Shy.

00:12:43.330 --> 00:12:46.066 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:12:50.771 --> 00:12:52.840 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clinking]

00:12:52.973 --> 00:12:54.475 position:21% line:89% align:start
After all this time,

00:12:55.175 --> 00:12:57.044 position:16% line:89% align:start
your feelings reached me.

00:12:58.245 --> 00:12:59.280 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mama.

00:12:59.980 --> 00:13:01.482 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
I'm sorry, Pesha.

00:13:01.849 --> 00:13:03.450 position:19% line:89% align:start
I haven't been myself.

00:13:04.952 --> 00:13:05.986 position:30% line:89% align:start
The sky's back.

00:13:06.353 --> 00:13:07.488 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[KUFUFU] Ook, ook?
-Huh?

00:13:07.622 --> 00:13:08.657 position:30% line:89% align:start
[cymbals clang]

00:13:09.089 --> 00:13:11.058 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KUFUFU]
Ook, ook ook!

00:13:11.191 --> 00:13:12.993 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
I know it's too late, sweetie,

00:13:13.695 --> 00:13:16.063 position:7% line:83% align:start
-but I have something to say--
-[KUFUFU] Tzveta, wait!

00:13:16.263 --> 00:13:17.998 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:13:18.198 --> 00:13:20.034 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[KUFUFU] It's not over yet!

00:13:20.167 --> 00:13:21.670 position:10% line:89% align:start
You can't give up so easily!

00:13:21.902 --> 00:13:24.972 position:7% line:83% align:start
I've still got a whole buncha'
contraptions up my sleeves!

00:13:25.105 --> 00:13:26.407 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[TZVETA] It's okay now.
-Huh?

00:13:26.741 --> 00:13:28.142 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
The fighting's over.

00:13:29.310 --> 00:13:31.478 position:38% line:83% align:start
I'm ready
for this dream to end.

00:13:31.979 --> 00:13:33.113 position:38% line:89% align:start
Not yet!

00:13:33.247 --> 00:13:34.481 position:35% line:83% align:start
If you let
your dream fade away,

00:13:34.616 --> 00:13:36.216 position:19% line:89% align:start
you'll disappear, too!

00:13:36.350 --> 00:13:37.384 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:37.951 --> 00:13:39.420 position:24% line:89% align:start
And I accept that.

00:13:39.788 --> 00:13:40.954 position:24% line:89% align:start
We can't stay here.

00:13:41.255 --> 00:13:43.190 position:10% line:89% align:start
Go make your way back to him.

00:13:44.258 --> 00:13:46.193 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's time to say goodbye.

00:13:47.328 --> 00:13:48.362 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:13:49.698 --> 00:13:50.765 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'll do that.

00:13:51.365 --> 00:13:54.401 position:19% line:83% align:start
But still, I won't say
goodbye to you.

00:13:54.536 --> 00:14:01.576 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:14:01.909 --> 00:14:04.612 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wind whooshing]

00:14:04.746 --> 00:14:05.780 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hold on.

00:14:05.946 --> 00:14:08.082 position:13% line:89% align:start
What she said, is it true?

00:14:09.751 --> 00:14:11.218 position:19% line:89% align:start
This space was my heart

00:14:11.352 --> 00:14:13.487 position:30% line:83% align:start
and everything
encompassed therein.

00:14:14.121 --> 00:14:15.790 position:33% line:83% align:start
When you look
at the person before you,

00:14:15.923 --> 00:14:18.793 position:7% line:83% align:start
you're looking at a mere image
made from that heart.

00:14:19.126 --> 00:14:22.630 position:21% line:83% align:start
So, after it's gone,
my body will also disappear.

00:14:22.764 --> 00:14:24.865 position:10% line:89% align:start
But why? Why can't you stay?

00:14:25.132 --> 00:14:28.302 position:19% line:83% align:start
After all these years,
we're finally together!

00:14:30.003 --> 00:14:31.872 position:10% line:89% align:start
You know, because of you two,

00:14:32.206 --> 00:14:33.407 position:13% line:89% align:start
I woke up from a nightmare

00:14:33.541 --> 00:14:35.677 position:27% line:83% align:start
that seemed like
it would go on forever.

00:14:36.210 --> 00:14:39.113 position:10% line:83% align:start
So please, there's something
you need to know.

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:40.280 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:14:40.981 --> 00:14:42.717 position:13% line:89% align:start
The person who created us,

00:14:43.217 --> 00:14:45.386 position:24% line:83% align:start
the child you refer
to as Stigma?

00:14:45.986 --> 00:14:47.287 position:27% line:89% align:start
I know his power.

00:14:47.488 --> 00:14:50.090 position:13% line:83% align:start
He can make other people's
dreams come true.

00:14:50.891 --> 00:14:52.960 position:19% line:89% align:start
But how can he do that?

00:14:53.828 --> 00:14:54.829 position:41% line:89% align:start
Simple.

00:14:54.962 --> 00:14:56.096 position:7% line:89% align:start
He can look into others' hearts

00:14:56.230 --> 00:14:57.699 position:33% line:83% align:start
and see what
they want the most.

00:14:58.165 --> 00:15:01.068 position:16% line:83% align:start
Then his power gives form
to that desire.

00:15:02.236 --> 00:15:04.972 position:13% line:83% align:start
It was because of his power
that we were reunited.

00:15:05.239 --> 00:15:07.007 position:19% line:89% align:start
It manifested me here.

00:15:08.208 --> 00:15:10.944 position:41% line:83% align:start
He knew
your dearest wish of all

00:15:11.078 --> 00:15:12.479 position:21% line:89% align:start
was to see me again.

00:15:12.980 --> 00:15:14.314 position:19% line:89% align:start
And he took advantage,

00:15:14.716 --> 00:15:17.719 position:7% line:83% align:start
making a twisted version of me
meant to harm you.

00:15:18.252 --> 00:15:19.754 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
He took it from me?

00:15:20.187 --> 00:15:21.422 position:21% line:89% align:start
So, he used his power

00:15:21.556 --> 00:15:23.858 position:27% line:83% align:start
to make Pepesha's
dream a reality?

00:15:24.358 --> 00:15:25.926 position:13% line:89% align:start
If he does that so easily,

00:15:26.093 --> 00:15:29.163 position:10% line:83% align:start
then what's the endgame that
Stigma's trying to bring about?

00:15:29.296 --> 00:15:32.065 position:19% line:83% align:start
That ability of his has
limitless possibilities.

00:15:33.735 --> 00:15:35.068 position:38% line:89% align:start
It does.

00:15:35.369 --> 00:15:37.971 position:19% line:83% align:start
And he wants to use it
to make a world without adults.

00:15:38.573 --> 00:15:40.742 position:7% line:89% align:start
A world made only for children.

00:15:41.509 --> 00:15:44.211 position:30% line:83% align:start
I followed him,
because I wanted the same.

00:15:45.747 --> 00:15:47.948 position:35% line:83% align:start
Of course,
there are restrictions.

00:15:48.449 --> 00:15:50.785 position:33% line:83% align:start
He can't make
his own dreams come true.

00:15:51.418 --> 00:15:53.954 position:13% line:83% align:start
His powers are meaningless
when he's on his own.

00:15:54.689 --> 00:15:58.125 position:24% line:83% align:start
And so...he created
a group of friends.

00:15:59.193 --> 00:16:02.630 position:16% line:83% align:start
That's where we come in,
Amarariruku.

00:16:03.397 --> 00:16:05.633 position:21% line:83% align:start
To start, he gave us
unique powers

00:16:05.767 --> 00:16:08.168 position:16% line:83% align:start
derived from what he saw
inside our hearts.

00:16:09.069 --> 00:16:12.540 position:19% line:83% align:start
We wanted to fight you,
but we needed equal footing.

00:16:13.708 --> 00:16:14.843 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shatters]

00:16:14.975 --> 00:16:16.744 position:30% line:83% align:start
Unfortunately,
that's all I know.

00:16:17.277 --> 00:16:19.814 position:38% line:83% align:start
I wonder,
what does he plan to do

00:16:19.948 --> 00:16:21.181 position:13% line:89% align:start
after he's taken this world

00:16:21.315 --> 00:16:23.450 position:24% line:83% align:start
and transfigured it
to fit his vision?

00:16:24.184 --> 00:16:26.521 position:35% line:83% align:start
That said,
one thing's for certain,

00:16:26.821 --> 00:16:28.989 position:19% line:83% align:start
his goal is to destroy
this world.

00:16:29.524 --> 00:16:32.192 position:21% line:83% align:start
As he warps one dream
after another.

00:16:33.193 --> 00:16:35.530 position:13% line:89% align:start
So please, I'm begging you.

00:16:35.830 --> 00:16:37.464 position:19% line:89% align:start
You have to stop them!

00:16:38.232 --> 00:16:41.401 position:30% line:83% align:start
They can't win!
Stigma can't take this world!

00:16:43.036 --> 00:16:45.105 position:27% line:83% align:start
This whole time,
I didn't notice.

00:16:45.807 --> 00:16:48.776 position:19% line:83% align:start
The fact that he warped
my heart past recognition,

00:16:49.343 --> 00:16:51.880 position:7% line:83% align:start
or the fact that I couldn't see
others around me.

00:16:52.112 --> 00:16:53.915 position:10% line:89% align:start
I was only looking at myself.

00:16:54.047 --> 00:16:55.282 position:35% line:89% align:start
Struggling.

00:16:56.149 --> 00:16:57.451 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:16:57.752 --> 00:16:59.954 position:24% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA] Excuse me,
please tell me your name again.

00:17:00.087 --> 00:17:03.525 position:24% line:83% align:start
Huh. Oh, I'm Teru.
Teru Momijiyama.

00:17:06.360 --> 00:17:09.062 position:16% line:89% align:start
Teru, dear, try to relax.

00:17:09.196 --> 00:17:10.497 position:21% line:89% align:start
You look so nervous.

00:17:10.932 --> 00:17:14.669 position:7% line:83% align:start
You know, your demeanor belies
the strength of your heart.

00:17:14.836 --> 00:17:18.272 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm impressed.
You're such a gentle soul.

00:17:18.940 --> 00:17:20.440 position:19% line:89% align:start
After all, without you,

00:17:20.575 --> 00:17:23.176 position:13% line:83% align:start
I would have never reunited
with my daughter.

00:17:23.477 --> 00:17:26.346 position:21% line:83% align:start
It was your kindness
that made it all possible.

00:17:27.281 --> 00:17:28.716 position:21% line:89% align:start
So, thank you, Teru.

00:17:29.082 --> 00:17:30.785 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh! It was nothing.

00:17:32.152 --> 00:17:33.855 position:30% line:89% align:start
Listen, Pesha,

00:17:34.656 --> 00:17:36.925 position:21% line:83% align:start
I want you to become
a guiding light.

00:17:37.457 --> 00:17:39.661 position:19% line:83% align:start
So go to the children,
and guide them.

00:17:39.794 --> 00:17:41.228 position:19% line:89% align:start
Teach what you believe.

00:17:41.696 --> 00:17:44.331 position:30% line:83% align:start
I've realized,
of all the things we can give,

00:17:44.766 --> 00:17:48.168 position:7% line:83% align:start
that's the best thing we adults
can offer to the future.

00:17:48.903 --> 00:17:50.137 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:17:51.673 --> 00:17:53.007 position:27% line:89% align:start
I believe in you.

00:17:53.541 --> 00:17:56.511 position:33% line:83% align:start
Now, I leave
this world's safety to you.

00:17:57.210 --> 00:17:59.479 position:19% line:89% align:start
Make me proud, Heroes.

00:18:00.949 --> 00:18:02.182 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Right!
-Right!

00:18:05.252 --> 00:18:06.654 position:38% line:89% align:start
Huh. No.

00:18:07.622 --> 00:18:08.856 position:35% line:89% align:start
Mama, wait.

00:18:09.724 --> 00:18:10.725 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's all right.

00:18:11.291 --> 00:18:13.595 position:30% line:83% align:start
I have sinned,
and even if my crimes

00:18:13.728 --> 00:18:16.731 position:13% line:83% align:start
were through Stigma's will,
I still acted on it.

00:18:17.097 --> 00:18:20.467 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm responsible for the damage
that I did to you two.

00:18:22.102 --> 00:18:23.905 position:24% line:89% align:start
But hey, it's okay.

00:18:24.505 --> 00:18:26.741 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you still call me mama
after everything,

00:18:26.874 --> 00:18:28.009 position:27% line:89% align:start
I haven't failed.

00:18:29.043 --> 00:18:32.780 position:16% line:83% align:start
So dear, I have one final
wish to ask of you.

00:18:33.615 --> 00:18:34.649 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:36.116 --> 00:18:37.150 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clinking]

00:18:38.052 --> 00:18:40.655 position:10% line:83% align:start
This has been a long-standing
dream of mine.

00:18:41.121 --> 00:18:43.925 position:16% line:83% align:start
To drink with my daughter
when she's all grown up...

00:18:44.692 --> 00:18:47.494 position:19% line:83% align:start
and see the incredible
woman she's become.

00:18:47.629 --> 00:18:53.467 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:18:53.601 --> 00:18:54.636 position:38% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:18:56.470 --> 00:18:58.305 position:7% line:89% align:start
You sure took your time, then.

00:18:58.573 --> 00:18:59.607 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:59.974 --> 00:19:02.744 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both laughing]

00:19:03.611 --> 00:19:06.581 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA] Pesha, have you been
making sure to eat enough?

00:19:07.081 --> 00:19:09.149 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Huh? Of course, I have.

00:19:09.416 --> 00:19:11.019 position:27% line:83% align:start
How do you think
I hold my liquor?

00:19:11.485 --> 00:19:13.121 position:30% line:89% align:start
Sure. I get it.

